'''性感象征'''（{{lang-en|sex symbol}}），指某一个著名的女性或男性被大众发现非常有[[性魅力|性魅力]]或非常有[[性吸引力|性吸引力]]，而成为性感的代言人<ref name=pam>[[Pam_Cook|Pam Cook]], "The trouble with sex: Diana Dors and the Blonde bombshell phenomenon", In: Bruce Babinigton (ed.), ''British Stars and Stardom: From Alma Taylor to Sean Connery'', [https://books.google.com/books?id=vxmQJRr0vL8C&pg=PA169 pp. 169–171] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vxmQJRr0vL8C&pg=PA169 |date=20201023175241 }}. Quote: "– the sex symbol is usually defined in terms of her excessive sexuality"</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dictionary.reference.com/browse/sex |title=''Word Origin & History'' |access-date=2019-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714224345/http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/sex |archive-date=2014-07-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

一般来说性感象征多是迎合[[异性恋|异性恋]]的，如果是迎合[[同性恋|同性恋]]的多称为[[同志偶像|同志偶像]]。

